{"tid":1677971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班黑警真係好驚死！個心好涼","createTime":"2019-10-27T11:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T13:39:42.000Z","uid":154116,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2df47110be873bdbd401058bfa36158ac8d66548","tid":1677971,"uid":154116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"利申：今日有要事，出唔到嚟。對唔住各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說，今日例牌各大巴士轉車站都駐重popp等拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就返屋企途中經過其中一個。然後，我見咁多所謂Madam/ 呀sir威風凜凜咁企撚哂係度，我緊係坐係巴士入面影低留念啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好笑係，當我完，佢地發現佢地個罩原來除低咗，然後鬼鬼祟祟帶返哂。然後，幾個吱吱朕，啤撚住我。個一下，我就緊係要眼神制敵啦，由上而下啤返佢地，用眼神話比佢地聽：「罷明影鳩你，上嚟拉鳩我囉。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個一刻，佢地眼神既空洞、無奈同淆底，真係好心涼。所有安全套都會有用完既一日，你班仆街知驚喇咩？怕死咩？學咩人帶罩？<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n諗返轉頭，其實而家影撚低哂佢地，等個法庭禁制令一完，咪一樣可以合法地公諸於世，到時班黑警咪一撚樣死。一係咁喇，唔爭在同法庭申請禁制令，連相都唔好撚比人影，咁咪唔撚洗驚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73243f09b1e64ee3255f12d5bbfd2739312d9107","tid":1677971,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:50:44.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3357802f6bc5995ed4c1749fb7e061e47ddb31ce","tid":1677971,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />影popo大頭"},{"pid":"65efdf4003dbd67fa291add5d562d11d258fa73c","tid":1677971,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:53:11.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c278105dc42175f54a06cbe44e99dbf0c6f38e","tid":1677971,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:53:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我譴責香港人戴口罩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得香港人厚此薄彼，<br />\n專針對優品360太無恥，<br />\n小商舖就敢搞，銀行就唔敢搞，<br />\n<br />\n18區都有銀行，都有優品360，偏偏厚此薄彼，<br />\n<br />\n戴口罩告暴動，<br />\n爆優品360告暴動，<br />\n爆銀行告暴動，偏偏厚此薄彼。<br />\n<br />\n利申，譴責一切暴力，<br />\n譴責爆銀行<br />\n譴責爆優品360<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">譴責香港人戴口罩</span></span>"},{"pid":"07a73594ad3667c2920fea059f85ea04acafb738","tid":1677971,"uid":53238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"精神勝利法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d6f3c05e0c05f1c87e7b04c43d1b7ab1801835","tid":1677971,"uid":154116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07a73594ad3667c2920fea059f85ea04acafb738","tid":1677971,"uid":53238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"精神勝利法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"要贏好多方法，我就係要佢地痴線，要佢地疑神疑鬼，唔會有完既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bbfdf5ece44b0e4edc375bad50feb1e9dfad7e","tid":1677971,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"大可以真係上黎拉你<br />\n<br />\n之後同車有手足就俾你條戇鳩仔累撚死"},{"pid":"09d1b17cf9a8cff971df0287c09c0bbcddd931fd","tid":1677971,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"和理非除左可以做哨兵做看更著黑衫截停狗隻，原來仲可以做參觀動物園既影相遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fea17d7160be01b2b2b2dd5449dd22fcf290f8e","tid":1677971,"uid":159448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:02:26.000Z","msg":